'''Seoul International Cafe Show''' is an annual coffee, tea, bakery and dessert event held at the [[COEX Convention & Exhibition Center]] in November in [[Gangnam District]], [[Seoul]], [[South Korea]]. In 2013, [[Memorandum of understanding|MOU]] signed between [[International Coffee Organization]] and Seoul International Cafe Show.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://us.aving.net/news/view.php?articleId=800934&mn_name=news|title=MOU Signed between International Coffee Organization and Seoul Int'l Cafe Show|last=|first=|date=March 5, 2014|website=aving.net|publisher=|access-date=2015-11-16}}</ref>
